---
// Contribute.astro
---

<div class="contribute" id="contributeSection">
  <h2>欢迎网友投稿分享！</h2>
  <div class="email-line">
    <span class="email-btn" onclick="openEmailModal()">admin@wvip.top</span>
  </div>
  <div class="note">
    我会认真查看每一封邮件，无论是否收录，都会诚挚地感谢您的分享！
  </div>
</div>

<style is:global>
  /* 感谢文字加大、加粗、提亮 */
  .contribute .note {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #b0b8c8;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
</style>